text.tspan: Specify the taxonomy of species involved in the data. You can
provide own taxonomic levels for the current taxonomy on
the right hand side. Just add with the plus button. Finally save
the current taxonomy description with the lower plus button.
Automatic assignment to taxonomy works with green fields.
You can also import a csv where the headers represent the ranks and the fields the names
Specify own rank. First set the
order of the item below one of
the left ranks. Then provide the
rank name and last the name.
